&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;At Submittable, we are transforming how organizations create social impact. Our platform empowers thousands of mission-driven organizations, from nonprofits to government entities, to make a difference in their communities and beyond. In 2024, our innovative software helped organizations worldwide run &lt;strong&gt;30,000 programs&lt;/strong&gt;, welcomed &lt;strong&gt;1.2 million applicants&lt;/strong&gt;, and facilitated the distribution of &lt;strong&gt;more than $10 billion&lt;/strong&gt; in funding through our products on behalf of our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
