&lt;p&gt;This is a full-time position that reports to the Director of Solutions Engineering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You&#39;ll Make an Impact&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a Trusted Advisor: Partner with prospects, customers, and stakeholders to ensure our solutions align with their technical and strategic goals, providing insights and recommendations that enhance both implementation and long-term outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the Technical Sales Process: Lead technical discovery, deliver compelling demos, build proofs of concept, and drive technical evaluations — ensuring seamless handoffs to Implementation and Customer Success teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create Strategic Solutions: Design tailored solutions that demonstrate the transformative potential of Submittable&#39;s Grants Management products for government and public sector customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster Collaboration: Work cross-functionally with Sales, Product, Engineering, and Customer Success to deliver holistic, scalable solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support RFP/RFI/RFQ Responses: In coordination with the Alliances and RFP Manager, assess solution fit, respond to functional and technical elements, coordinate security questionnaires, and provide demonstrations and follow-up documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Pre-Sales Documentation &amp;amp; SOWs: Lead the creation of high-quality pre-sales documentation and Statements of Work that accurately scope projects and set customers up for success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Elevate the Practice: Develop and refine tools, processes, and collateral to advance our Solutions Engineering capabilities and improve scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inspire Action: Represent Submittable at conferences, webinars, and external engagements to highlight our mission and showcase the impact of our solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain Expert-Level Platform Knowledge: Become a true product expert — understanding how Submittable&#39;s solutions solve customer problems and deliver value, with a commitment to continuous self-learning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel: Be available to travel up to 25% of the time for on-site prospect and customer engagements.&lt;/li&gt;

